description:
This is a ticket for a raffle to win this as an asset for musical production and composition


The only way to get the final asset with its individual parts is entering a raffle
where it must be needed to create an original piece of music using the musical ideas and motives from here. it will be
needed to produce them exclusively within a metal or electronic music context (including subgenres). This would
count as an entry for each wallet*

*You would need to contact me via:  https://twitter.com/Symctrae
to show me your work and transfer you the entry for the raffle


Once that there are 2 entries, a countdown of a random number of days will start (within 7 days)
After the countdown is over the raffle will run and will determine a winner who will be able to use this asset
as part of its own library for their own creations and will also win a secret visual loop + a different 
version of the original track for use as an additional asset...

||||The track works as an asset for producers to use in their own compositions (it's made that way so it can be 
sampled or edited using a plugin too, aplying different effects and filters).
